#eNCA's Moloko Moloto follows the story. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The search continues for a tiger in the South of Johannesburg. The female tiger escaped from its cage on Saturday night. It has since attacked a man and a dog in the Walkerville area. Female tiger on the loose south of Johannesburg The family of the man are threatening legal action. Meanwhile, residents in the area are urged to be on high alert. eNCA's Moloko Moloto has the details in the video above. 